it.apice.sapere.node.agents.impl This package contains the SAPEREagents implementations. 
it.apice.sapere.node.internal This package contains the Bundle Activator and other utilities. 
it.apice.sapere.node.networking.guestsmngt.impl This package contains entities dedicated to Guests handling. 
it.apice.sapere.node.networking.obsnotif.impl This package contains the subsystem dedicated to the notification (and management) of remote observation of LSA-space events. 
it.apice.sapere.node.networking.utils.impl This package contains some utility classes for networking handling. 
it.apice.sapere.space This package contains it.apice.sapere.space entities tests. 
it.apice.sapere.space.avoid This package contains utilities for bundle access outside an OSGi context. 
it.apice.sapere.space.impl This package contains the implementation of the services required to handle an LSA-space (.space). 
it.apice.sapere.space.observation.impl This package contains the implementation of the services required to handle an LSA-space (.space.observation).
